io.dropwizard.jackson

Class AnnotationSensitivePropertyNamingStrategy

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.PropertyNamingStrategy
      • io.dropwizard.jackson.AnnotationSensitivePropertyNamingStrategy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class AnnotationSensitivePropertyNamingStrategy
extends com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.PropertyNamingStrategy
    A PropertyNamingStrategy implementation which, if the declaring class of a property is annotated with JsonSnakeCase, uses a PropertyNamingStrategy.LowerCaseWithUnderscoresStrategy, and uses the default PropertyNamingStrategy otherwise.
    See Also:
